headline: Duke Energy Foundation helps make Florida's natural resources more resilient with $285,000 in grants
summary: Today, the Duke Energy Foundation announced $285,000 in grants to support the environmental vitality and resiliency of communities across Florida. Ten environmentally focused organizations will receive funding to continue Duke Energy's investment in the state's natural resources.
